                    <span>After looking for a decent book on copywriting on Amazon (where else?), I decided to buy this one, based on the positive reviews it got from other readers. And, I must say, they were right. This is an excellent book if you want to learn the basics of copywriting and start off as a freelancer!</span>
                  
              
